         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to request in the name of the Board of Governors of the Botanic Gardens Adelaide, that you will please to inform me by post at your earliest convenience, as follows ¶  ¶ On w...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.12.00d</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Francis</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">GRG/70/1/1 Letter book of the Botanic Gardens Committee, State Records, South Australia.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Item is a file copy, unsigned, of a letter that would have been sent<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to each of the recipients<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by Francis,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>who was instructed to write it at the meeting of the Board of Governors held on 14<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>December 1860<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(minute book 1855-1875, Adelaide Botanic Gardens).</p>
               </note>Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to request in the name of the Board of Governors of the Botanic Gardens Adelaide, that you will please to inform me by post at your earliest convenience, as follows</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On what days of the week and what hours of the day are the Gardens at __ open to the public, and if your garden be only open during certain days and hours, what is the reason that the attendance is confined to such times</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I am Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c &amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Directors Bot. Gardens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, Hobarton, Sydney, Launceston</p>
         </div>
